T1  - Interorganizational Dependence and Control as Predictors of Opportunism in Dealer-Supplier Relations
AU  - Provan, Keith G.
AU  - Skinner, Steven J.
Y1  - 1989/03/01
PY  - 1989
DA  - 1989/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256427
